item.description:
Love seafood? Then reward yourself with a trip to Maine. Maine Fish Market Restaurant in East Windsor Connecticut!

Their just-off-the-boat seafood will indulge your pallet with tender lobster, succulent shrimp, and your favorite fish, broiled to absolute perfection. And, now's your chance to enjoy even more of what you love.

Explore the dinner menu to discover seafood like you've never tasted. From succulent Pan-Seared Crab Cakes to fresh Atlantic Salmon...chef's latest creations are sure to tantalize your taste buds. And, of course, all your traditional favorites are waiting on you, too. Here is the menu...

http://www.mainefishmarket.com/pdf/mainefishmarket_dinner_color.pdf

Join us for a great seafood adventure. Yummy food and great conversation...indulge yourself. Come on out and test the waters!!!
item.how_to_find_us: Look for Terri or the Meetup Sign...cell is 203-808-5829
